title: Honda Astrea Supra 100  '10
description: Polite to sigkekrimeno mixanaki..sta xartia einai honda supra 100 kai o skeletos einai gnisios...to kalokairi to ekana anakataskevi kainouria plastika fanaria konter..moter lifan 110 kai ta xristougena tou rvala kaimouries zantes lastixa kai alisidofranaza ...to mixanaki einai prosegmeno tou alazo ta ladia kathe mina kai den koinite kathimerina - Less -
